{
  "texts": [
    "In a few other cases, researchers were reluctant to hand over writing to AI because it is a task they excel at and enjoy.",
    "One professor in engineering explained that \"it's kind of funny.",
    "I actually enjoy writing even in my spare time.",
    "I enjoy writing and so it's a task that I don't really want to give away to AI and try to do it myself, because it's something I enjoy doing.\"",
    "An important caveat is that several interviewees indicated that they frequently saw AI-generated text submitted to journals in their field and suspected many of their colleagues were using AI to generate text."
  ]
}